lyrics:
[verse]
In the land of law and order, a tale unfolds
A naked landlord claiming rights untold
But the truth remains, this argument untrue
No justification for lower rent will do

[chorus]
German court, stand firm, hold your ground
Expose the lies with justice profound
No nudity will sway your decree
Fair rent prevails, for all to see
